                2 {
                  1: "Description"
                  2: "<p>The Hocco Hazelnut Mudslide Cone Ice Cream combines the rich, nutty flavour of hazelnuts with a creamy, chocolatey base. This indulgent dessert offers the perfect balance of sweet and nutty, all served in a crispy cone. It\'s a luxurious ice cream experience for anyone who loves chocolate and hazelnuts together.</p> \n<ul> \n<li><strong>Nutty Hazelnut flavour</strong>: This ice cream is infused with the bold flavour of roasted hazelnuts, providing a delicious nutty taste that complements the creamy chocolate base. The hazelnut flavour is distinct and rich, adding a satisfying depth to the ice cream. It\342\200\231s the perfect treat for hazelnut lovers, who will enjoy the nutty undertones in every bite. The roasted hazelnuts contribute a warm, earthy flavour, enhancing the overall richness of the ice cream and providing a decadent experience that makes this dessert feel both luxurious and comforting.</li> \n<li><strong>Chocolatey Mudslide Base</strong>: The chocolatey mudslide base is rich, smooth and indulgent, offering a creamy texture that perfectly balances the nuttiness of the hazelnuts. This chocolate base is the perfect partner for the hazelnut flavour, creating a harmonious blend of flavours that are both satisfying and decadent. The richness of the chocolate is complemented by the crunch of the hazelnuts, creating a delightful contrast of textures. The combination of chocolate and hazelnuts makes this ice cream a treat for anyone who enjoys the best of both worlds in a single cone.</li> \n<li><strong>Crispy Cone</strong>: This ice cream is served in a crispy cone that adds a satisfying crunch to each bite. The cone provides a perfect contrast to the smooth and creamy ice cream, giving you a variety of textures in every mouthful. It\342\200\231s light yet sturdy enough to hold the rich ice cream without breaking. The cone enhances the overall indulgence, making the experience of enjoying this ice cream even more enjoyable. It\342\200\231s a great way to enjoy your favorite ice cream while also getting the satisfying crunch of a quality cone with every bite.</li> \n</ul> \n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Returns And Refund Policy:</strong></li></ul>\n<ul><li>- This item is eligible for a refund within 3 days of purchase in the unlikely event of a damaged, defective, or incorrect item.</li><li>- In case of an incorrect item, a refund or replacement request can be raised only if the item is sealed, unopened, and unused.</li></ul>"
